ode 底层技术全景导览\",\"url\":\"https://time.geekbang.org/column/article/942438?noteid=15724821\"},{\"title\":\"10个最好的Vibe编码工具 (2026)\",\"url\":\"https://m.toutiao.com/a7603253277504897551/\"},{\"title\":\"8 个好用的 AI 编程工具(助手)推荐\",\"url\":\"https://apifox.com/apiskills/ai-code-tools/\"},{\"title\":\"编程变天了！最全 AI Coding 工具地图（含国内外下载全路径）\",\"url\":\"https://post.m.smzdm.com/p/amoq0p4v/\"},{\"title\":\"2026 年 10 款好用的 VSCode 代码补全插件推荐\",\"url\":\"https://apifox.com/apiskills/vscode-code-completion/\"},{\"title\":\"Install Windsurf IDE on Android Termux & ARM64 Linux - GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/MaheshTechnicals/Windsurf-Termux\"},{\"title\":\"IDE进化论：Windsurf 如何重新定义开发者工作流与AI集成体验\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/mongodb5scout/article/details/156249548\"}]\n\nBased on my search results, I couldn't find any specific information about **\"Devin 2.0\"** or **\"Windsurf Wave 4\"** being announced in February 2026. However, I did find extensive information about current versions and developments of these AI coding tools. Let me summarize what I found:\n\n## **Devin / Cognition.AI**\n- **Current Status**: Devin (version 1.x) is Cognition.AI's flagship \"AI software engineer\" product\n- **Key News from Feb 2026**: Cognition.AI acquired Windsurf's remaining assets from OpenAI, absorbing ~200 employees and gaining enterprise customers with $82M ARR\n- **Capabilities**: End-to-end autonomous software development, not just code completion\n- **Valuation**: Cognition.AI reportedly valued at over $10 billion\n\n## **Windsurf (by Codeium)**\n- **No \"Wave 4\" found** - Current documentation refers to Windsurf as an AI-native IDE\n- **Acquisition Context**: Windsurf was originally going to be acquired by OpenAI in 2025, but the deal was blocked by Microsoft. Google then acquired the core team for $2.4B valuation, while Cognition picked up the remaining assets\n- **Key Features**: Cascade Agentic assistant, remote cloud indexing for large codebases (1M+ lines), multi-file editing\n\n## **Cursor IDE**\n- **Latest Version**: v2.4.x series (February 2026)\n- **February 2026 Update**: Released Composer 1.5 model with improved code generation accuracy and speed\n- **Recent Features**: \n  - Shadow Workspace (background intent prediction)\n  - Plan Mode (design before coding)\n  - Subagents (parallel multi-agent workflow)\n  - Support for 8 parallel agents\n\n## **Important Notes:**\n- The search results don't show any official announcements for \"Devin 2.0\" or \"Windsurf Wave 4\"\n- These version names may be:\n  - Internal development names not yet public\n  - Rumored/speculative releases\n  - Misconceptions about existing features\n- The results are primarily from Chinese tech news sources and developer communities from February 2026\n\n**Recommendation**: If you're looking for specific information about these version releases, you may want to check official company announcements from Cognition.AI, Codeium/Windsurf, or Cursor directly, or search for press releases from late February 2026.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
