dit, Chat, and Agent modes\n\n### **Aider**\n- Terminal-based AI coding tool\n- Git integration with automatic commit messages\n- Voice coding support\n- Multi-file editing capabilities\n\n---\n\n**Important Note**: The search results contain some inconsistencies with dates (some mentioning 2026 dates for what should be 2025 events). For the most accurate and up-to-date February 2025 changelogs, I recommend checking directly with each tool's official documentation:\n\n- **Claude Code**: docs.anthropic.com\n- **Cursor**: cursor.com or cursor.sh\n- **GitHub Copilot**: github.com/features/copilot\n- **Windsurf**: codeium.com\n- **Devin**: cognition.ai\n\nWould you like me to search for more specific information about any particular tool?"
